Area 3 — Token-budget vs max-turns precedence (2 tests):
  - TestTester_TokenWinsOverMaxTurns: 500-token context (threshold 425),
    100 tokens/call. Halts after 5 main + 1 delta = 6 calls with
    HaltTokenLimit. PASS.
  - TestTester_MaxTurnsBackstopWithSlowTokens: 1M token context, 0-token
    responses. Fires HaltMaxTurns after 50 main + 10 delta = 60 calls. PASS.
  Confirmed: token-budget check binds before HaltMaxTurns when crossing
